.DT
set_feature_chats
Disk World creator help
set_feature_chats

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_feature_chats -  This method is used to add room chats to locations that can view a particular feature.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_feature_chats(string title,
mixed * chats,
mixed * night_chats)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^title%^RESET%^ - the name of the feature
%^BOLD%^chats%^RESET%^ - an array of strings (room chats related to the feature)
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/terrain_map/handler_base.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is used to add room chats to locations that can view a
particular feature. $D substitution is carried out on the chats.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
add_feature, modify_feature, room_chat

.EP

